Advantages of This Stored Procedure Version
Fully parameterized: source table, partition column, batch size, parallelism.
Uses shadow table + stage table → zero downtime.
Batch insert + partition SWITCH → fast migration for hundreds of millions of rows.
Parallel partition processing reduces total migration time.
Delta catch-up ensures changes during migration are applied.
All nonclustered indexes are recreated dynamically.
Final table swap is metadata-only → downtime < 5 seconds.
Can be called repeatedly for multiple tables or migrations.